    "• The inconsistency of the Arabic language, particularly concerning similar stroke characters and dots, can be lost or deleted due to low resolution or preprocessing.",
    "This issue is particularly pertinent for characters with diacritical marks, which require more attention and investigation.Addressing these challenges will require further research and development in the field of AHR, including the development of new techniques for preprocessing, feature extraction, and architecture design, as well as the creation of larger and more diverse labeled datasets.",
    "There are several potential directions for the future application of CNNs in AHR.Here are some possibilities:• Improving recognition accuracy: Despite the promising results achieved by CNNbased models in AHR, there is still room for improving their recognition accuracy.",
    "Future research could explore ways to enhance the training process by optimizing hyperparameters and developing more effective loss functions.",
    "• Hybrid state-of-the-art models have demonstrated significant improvements in AHR compared to standard models."
